headline: CME Group Futures to Launch on Robinhood, Bringing New Trading Opportunities to Retail Investors
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, and Robinhood Derivatives, LLC ('Robinhood'), today announced that some of CME Group's most popular futures products have started rolling out on the Robinhood mobile app.
